#. type: YAML Front Matter: title
#: upstream/_posts/2021-06-22-abraxas-customer-story.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Java and Taxes: Two Things That Are Certain in a Developer's Life"
msgstr ""

#. type: Target for macro image
